abstract: vanguard international dividend appreciation etf plans $ 0.26 quarterly dividend .
article: vanguard international dividend appreciation etf declared a quarterly dividend on tuesday , december 19th , wall street journal reports . shareholders of record on wednesday , december 20th will be paid a dividend of 0.2586 per share on friday , december 22nd . this represents a $ 1.03 dividend on an annualized basis and a yield of 1.58 % . the ex-dividend date of this dividend is tuesday , december 19th . shares of vanguard international dividend appreciation etf traded down $ 0.36 on tuesday , reaching $ 65.39 . the company 's stock had a trading volume of 81,000 shares , compared to its average volume of 80,431 .
